title: Story
content:
Some mistakes get made
That's alright, that's okay
You can think that you're in love
When you're really just in pain
Some mistakes get made
That's alright, that's okay In the end, it's better for me
That's the moral of the story, babe
author: Molina

title: get the hell out
content:
너를 떠올리는 것,
찌를 듯이 아픈 것 잊혀지지 않는 건, 내겐 저주 같은 것 하루만,
잠시만 지울 수 있다면 내 세상은 더 아름다울 것 같은데
author: Molina
